title: AIMS, Kabul City River Shapefiles, Afghanistan, 2004
name: AIMS, Kabul City River Shapefiles, Afghanistan, 2004
description:
Abstract:
        The Kabul city river layer was digitized from IKONOS satellite imagery (2000-2002) at 1:5,000 scale. This layer includes 1 type of river. 
    Purpose:
        Kabul city river layers provide basemap data on river features at a 1:5,000 scale. Users must assume responsibility in determining the usability of this data for their purpose. Not for use in scales greater than 1:5,000.
